dmedak: 5th tournament of the 7th Season of Croatian School Go League.
dmedak: 7 years ago, we had one player who was the only single digit kyu (9kyu) and 20 players in the range of 16-20 kyu.
dmedak: Now we have 4 strong dan players and 4 strong single digit players, with many beginners following them.
dmedak: About the place: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Veliki_Gr%C4%91evac
dmedak: "Veliki Grdjevac" is a small town where everyone knows about the game of go, thanks to two 5 dan players (Kuhar brothers) who were spreading the game for decades.
